VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.(query|execute)\(\s*`|\$where\s*:\s*|sequelize\.query\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:prepare|parameterize|\?.*params|TypeORM.*QueryBuilder|createQueryBuilder
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects query construction patterns requiring injection review.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Angular SQL/NoSQL Injection Sink.
